    VANESSA You know what? This isn\u2019t so hard. Vanessa pretends to HONK THE
    HORN. VANESSA (CONT\u2019D) Beep, beep! Beep, beep! A BOLT OF LIGHTNING HITS
    the plane. The plane takes a sharp dip. VANESSA (CONT\u2019D) Barry, what happened?
    BARRY (noticing the control panel) Wait a minute. I think we were on autopilot
    that whole time. VANESSA That may have been helping me. BARRY And now we\u2019re
    not! VANESSA (V.O.) (folding her arms) Well, then it turns out I cannot fly a
