    TO: EXT. AIRPLANE A GIGANTIC SWARM OF BEES flies in to hold the plane up. CUT
    TO: INT. COCKPIT - CONTINUOUS BARRY You snap out of it! VANESSA You snap out
    of it! \"Bee Movie\" - JS REVISIONS 8/13/07 120. BARRY You snap-- VANESSA Hold
